<TEXT>
<P>
How refreshing to learn of Lampel's means of gaining Cranston's attention when 
no other conventional method prevailed. Surely the honorable senator, having 
been backed into a corner by Lampel, could do better than to offer assistance 
of a further bailout possibility by the federal government from a problem which 
