<SUBJECT>
<P>
DROUGHTS -- CALIFORNIA; CONSERVATION; RAIN -- CALIFORNIA; WATER -- CALIFORNIA; 
RAIN; DROUGHTS -- SANTA BARBARA COUNTY; WATER SHORTAGES 
</P>
