GOVERNMENT; DEMONSTRATIONS -- ROMANIA; COMMUNIST PARTY (ROMANIA); COUNCIL OF 
THE FRONT OF NATIONAL SALVATION; GOVERNMENT REFORM; CEAUSESCU, NICOLAE 
</P>
