TRAFFICKING -- PANAMA; MEDELLIN CARTEL; MONEY LAUNDERING; CENTRAL INTELLIGENCE 
AGENCY; SEARCH AND SEIZURE; DRUG SEIZURES; NORIEGA, MANUEL A 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
