LINCOLN SAVINGS &amp; LOAN ASSOCIATION; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; AMERICAN 
CONTINENTAL CORP; CRANSTON, ALAN; KEATING, CHARLES H JR; WILSON, PETE 
</P>
